a new connection is made for every csv file (at the beginning of each import_csv_file.php)

there is no PHP error, nothing logged in mongod.log, nor in /var/log/messages, the script is still running, but it's just doing nothing

the process goes like this:

cron job calls import_feeds.php every minute (it can run only one instance at a time, i use a shell script to check)
- import_feeds.php gets 20 CSV files (feeds) to be processed
- import_feeds.php calls import_csv_file.php for each CSV file
    - import_csv_file.php then:
